public class MonitorAttributeMapperImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.orbitz.monitoring.api.mappers.MonitorAttributeMapper

By default, this class maps String, Number, Date, Boolean, Collection, Map and Array. The mapper also accepts custom ObjectAttributeMapper. Currently does not support nested Collection, Map and Array.
